BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, June 6 (XINHUA) -- Chinese Vice-Premier Li 
Lanqing met here today with Shi Hian-chen, a Thai-Chinese and 
vice-chairman of the Society for the Promotion of the Chinese 
Culture. 
  During their meeting the host and guest had a discussion on 
how to help Chinese children in poor areas to go to school. 

